1.8
log
@formatting errors, found using freebsd's "igor";
@
text
@.\" $OpenBSD: inb.2,v 1.7 2007/05/31 19:19:27 jmc Exp $
.\"
.\" Copyright (c) 2002 Matthieu Herrb
.\" All rights reserved.
